title: Grateful Dead Live at Giants Stadium on 1989-07-10
description:
Set 1

Feel Like A Stranger-> Franklin's Tower, Walkin' Blues, Jack A Roe, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Tennessee Jed, The Music Never Stopped-> Don't Ease Me In

Set 2

Foolish Heart, A Little Light, Playin->UJB->Drumz*->Iko Iko*->Watchtower*->Morning Dew*->Sugar Magnolia* E:Heaven's Door*

* w/ guitarist, drummer & keyboard player from Neville Bros.
